When comparing identical armory loads/buffs/options on the same character, Rawr3 vs 2.3.13 shows a huge disparity in the effective DPS for Deathbringer's Will and Whispering Fanged Skull for both ilvls with Rawr3 being substantially lower. Most other trinkets absolute values for DPS are in the ballpark (+/-3dps).  Needle-encrusted Scorpion is slightly higher in Rawr3 (486 vs 464).  Attached is the .xml.
 
Thanks for everything and keep up the great work.
